Hi @Lloyd useAsTitle does not support nested fields currently, we will commonly use a virtual field to get specific data for your document title. For example:<br><br><pre><code class="hljs">    {
      name: &#x27;title&#x27;,
      type: &#x27;text&#x27;,
      admin: {
        hidden: true,
      },
      hooks: {
        beforeChange: [
          ({ data }) =&gt; {
